HEADWORD: hand-operated
<hw>hand-operated</hw> <pos>adj.</pos> <sn>1.</sn> <def>requiring hand
manipulation for operation; not automatic or machine-driven; <as>as, a
<ex>hand-operated</ex> winch</as>. Opposite of <ant>automatic</ant> or
<ant>powered</ant>.</def>⟦br⟧
<syn><b>Syn. --</b> non-automatic.</syn>⟦br⟧
[<source>WordNet 1.5</source>]</p>

